cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing techniques and deep learning-based text classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the vulnerabilities of deep neural networks, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The optimization algorithm used in the paper is related to machine learning, which is covered by cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the potential impact on artificial intelligence, which could be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
